-- ALTER VIEW kpiemail.dim_coaching
-- AS
SELECT
[CICLO]
,[TERRITORIO_GD]
,[TOTAL_COACHING]
,[TOTAL_ABATER]
,[DIAS_UTEIS_COACHING]
,[KEY_CICLO_TERR_GD]
FROM
    OPENROWSET(
        BULK 'https://gsksynapseaccount.dfs.core.windows.net/gskoutputfiles/Email & KPI Visitacao/dimensao_coaching.parquet',
        FORMAT='PARQUET'
    ) WITH (
[CICLO]                  VARCHAR(10) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[TERRITORIO_GD]		VARCHAR(25) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[TOTAL_COACHING]		VARCHAR(25) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[TOTAL_ABATER]			VARCHAR(25) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[DIAS_UTEIS_COACHING]	VARCHAR(25) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[KEY_CICLO_TERR_GD]	VARCHAR(25) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
    ) AS ROW
